SADOMASOCHIST DETECTIVE.
Written by Guido Barsi and art by Locomotion Gonzalez.

Alex is one of the most respected detectives in the city and the country. She has solved major cases that have earned her an important reputation, in addition to being the daughter of a family of police officers. But Alex also has a secret: she is a sex addict, a lover of sadomasochism, and cannot help but seek to be degraded and take sex to the extreme in situations that put her career and life at risk. When a killer threatens the peace of the city, Alex's worst fears seem to come true when the killer starts threatening to reveal the truth, and she cannot help but feel even more excited.
